Repeat: yo, knit 3, pass the yo loop over the 3 stitches just knitted; sl 3 wyif
yo, knit 3, pass the yo loop over the 3 stitches just knitted; p3
with right needle, lift loop of next wrap (below and to the left) onto the left needle, knit the loop together with the next stitch; k5
sl 3 wyif; yo, knit 3, pass the yo loop over the 3 stitches just knitted
p3; yo, knit 3, pass the yo loop over the 3 stitches just knitted
with right needle, lift loop of next wrap (below and to the left) onto the left needle, knit the loop together with the next stitch; k5
